ection=3D9" title=3D"Edit section: Computing the null distribution"><span>e=
dit</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>Computing <i>p</i>-values requires knowing the distribution of <span cla=
ss=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mat=
hml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"ht=
